INSTALLING:

iegen uses a python based build system called waf.

Use the following commands to configure, build, and install iegen:

1)     ./waf configure --prefix=location_to_install_to --polylib-loc=path_to_polylib --cloog-loc=path_to_cloog
  (ex: ./waf configure --prefix=$PWD --polylib-loc=$HOME/software/polylib/ --cloog-loc=$HOME/software/cloog)

2) ./waf build

3) ./waf install
